{"tha-ap58:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap58:0.2":"Bijanivagga ","tha-ap58:0.3":"Saparivarasanattheraapadana ","tha-ap58:1.1":"“Padumuttarabuddhassa, ","tha-ap58:1.2":"pindapatam adasaham; ","tha-ap58:1.3":"Gantva kilitthakam thanam, ","tha-ap58:1.4":"mallikahi parikkhitam. ","tha-ap58:2.1":"Tamhasanamhi asino, ","tha-ap58:2.2":"buddho lokagganayako; ","tha-ap58:2.3":"Akittayi pindapatam, ","tha-ap58:2.4":"ujubhuto samahito. ","tha-ap58:3.1":"Yathapi bhaddake khette, ","tha-ap58:3.2":"bijam appampi ropitam; ","tha-ap58:3.3":"Samma dharam pavecchante, ","tha-ap58:3.4":"phalam toseti kassakam. ","tha-ap58:4.1":"Tathevayam pindapato, ","tha-ap58:4.2":"sukhette ropito taya; ","tha-ap58:4.3":"Bhave nibbattamanamhi, ","tha-ap58:4.4":"phalam te tosayissati. ","tha-ap58:5.1":"Idam vatvana sambuddho, ","tha-ap58:5.2":"jalajuttamanamako; ","tha-ap58:5.3":"Pindapatam gahetvana, ","tha-ap58:5.4":"pakkami uttaramukho. ","tha-ap58:6.1":"Samvuto patimokkhasmim, ","tha-ap58:6.2":"indriyesu ca pancasu; ","tha-ap58:6.3":"Pavivekamanuyutto, ","tha-ap58:6.4":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap58:7.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap58:7.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap58:7.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap58:8.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma saparivarasano thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap58:9.1":"Saparivarasanattherassapadanam chattham. "}